{"id": "1487043503652602007", "channel_id": "1485672193634467960", "type": 19, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "前面我也贊同\n自選的話 我會覺得抽C不如抽輔助\n墨菲 詩人1啟就夠\n羊媽 也只要2啟\n怎麼抽都不會虧", "timestamp": "2026-03-27T10:59:59.203000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["400656449417773066"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1487041372023160843", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
